Power Struggle
---

Two people or groups fight for control. Real, external stakes loom over the struggle. An outcome in favor of the antagonist should spell absolute disaster for the protagonist. 

- __Mutiny.__ (Summary of “Bots of the Lost Arc” by Suzanne Palmer)A group of humans are in stasis aboard a ship. Malfunctioning bots have initiated a mutiny, bestowing personhood upon themselves. The ship and a single loyal bot must defeat the mutineers and wake the crew before the ship reaches the territory of an alien species that considers uncontrolled artificial life forms as a social evil that should be destroyed.

